{"tid":813480,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住一個女仔，好想同佢講地對唔住","createTime":"2018-09-10T12:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T05:26:44.000Z","uid":197813,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8194d09e91e885ecf42a12fc4785735aed8cfd","tid":813480,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:49:32.000Z","msg":"曾經有一個好愛我既女仔<br />\n雖然係網上面識，識左一年有多<br />\n但佢亦係唯一一個比Ex更著緊我，會秒回我<br />\n會關心我既女仔，雖然大家係網上面識，但都曖昧到跟本同男女朋友一樣，會晚晚揾我傾電話，又會開cam傾計<br />\n<br />\n但到最後，我都無同到佢一齊，因為佢係澳門人，係，我地真人係無見過<br />\n<br />\n佢曾經都話等佢多一個月，考埋試就會過黎揾我，一齊去玩，住幾日酒店。<br />\n<br />\n但到最後，我都係等唔到佢，係佢考完試之後，同佢坦白左<br />\n<br />\n我接受唔到Long D，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢喊左成晚，wts call左我7次&hellip;&hellip;唉，唔想講了<br />\n<br />\n好內疚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df8c57891627c4ee10e1c5653d9748cbd537ece","tid":813480,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T12:59:33.000Z","msg":"毒絲開Post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f59d153bf99405e9614ebbf3ed6c422b308385","tid":813480,"uid":15243,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"澳門都long d 收皮啦"},{"pid":"8a3ec88581905b2075850565e37a16f354065d66","tid":813480,"uid":197813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c9f59d153bf99405e9614ebbf3ed6c422b308385","tid":813480,"uid":15243,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"澳門都long d 收皮啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:04:18.000Z","msg":"對於我黎講，係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f98987e01445575d2abc9e7460327947f9781e19","tid":813480,"uid":128158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:09:26.000Z","msg":"坐船過去先一個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c